。感谢这张迷你专辑，所有的目光将继续集中在他们身上，我们非常兴奋地看到他们接下来的去向。”</p><p>其他新闻方面，New Jeans 最近凭借<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newjeans-get-up-asap-music-video-release-3473520">《Get Up》</a>击败全明星<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/barbie"><em>芭比</em></a>原声带， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newjeans-beat-barbie-soundtrack-debut-number-one-billboard-200-3477500">在 Billboard 200 排行榜上夺得了他们的第一张排行榜冠军专辑</a>。</p><p>这五人组合是继去年 9 月<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blackpink">BLACKPINK</a>推出“Born Pink”之后第二个获得此殊荣的韩国流行女团。</p><p>他们最近还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/hear-newjeans-change-up-cool-with-you-with-a-live-band-3476903">分享了由现场乐队伴奏的新单曲“Cool With You”的表演</a>。</p><p>该表演是与韩国流行音乐 YouTube 系列<em>It’s Live 合作的。</em>成员们的声音仍然忠于原作，尽管现场乐器演奏更加乐观。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newjeans-on-billie-eilish-at-lollapalooza-we-love-her-energy-and-her-songs-3477907">NewJeans 通过观看 Billie Eilish 为 Lollapalooza 做准备：“我们爱她的能量”的帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
社交媒体对“杀手树懒”恐怖电影《树懒屋》预告片的反应：“电影院又回来了” https://www.nme.com/news/film/social-media-reacts-to-trailer-for-killer-sloth-horror-movie-slotherhouse-cinema-is-so-back-3477900?utm_source=rss&utm_medium= rss&utm_campaign=社交媒体对树懒杀手恐怖电影树懒电影预告片的反应Hollie GeraghtyThu, 03 Aug 2023 20:59:29 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3477900 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/slotherhouse-trailer-killer-sloth.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="斯洛瑟豪斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/slotherhouse-trailer-killer-sloth.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/slotherhouse-trailer-killer-sloth-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/slotherhouse-trailer-killer-sloth-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/slotherhouse-trailer-killer-sloth-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/slotherhouse-trailer-killer-sloth-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/slotherhouse-trailer-killer-sloth-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “你让我看了树懒杀手恐怖电影”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/social-media-reacts-to-trailer-for-killer-sloth-horror-movie-slotherhouse-cinema-is-so-back-3477900">社交媒体对“杀手树懒”恐怖电影“Slotherhouse”预告片的反应：“电影院又回来了”</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/slotherhouse-trailer-killer-sloth.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="斯洛瑟豪斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/slotherhouse-trailer-killer-sloth.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/slotherhouse-trailer-killer-sloth-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/slotherhouse-trailer-killer-sloth-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/slotherhouse-trailer-killer-sloth-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/slotherhouse-trailer-killer-sloth-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/slotherhouse-trailer-killer-sloth-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>一部关于名为<em>《Slotherhouse》</em>的“杀手树懒”的新恐怖电影的预告片已经发布，让社交媒体用户感到困惑和好笑。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/cocaine-bear-review-3403322">《可卡因熊》评论：今年最狂野的电影中的搞砸和毛茸茸的</a></strong></li></ul><p>追随<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/cocaine-bear-review-3403322">《可卡因熊》</a></em> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/cocaine-shark-trailer-watch-the-chaotic-introduction-to-jaws-on-drugs-3411391"><em>《可卡因</em><em>鲨鱼》</em></a>和<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/social-media-reacts-to-crackcoon-trailer-cocaine-bear-has-nothing-on-the-crackoon-3452179">《裂纹浣熊》</a></em>等电影的脚步，<em>斯洛瑟豪斯</em>向日益流行的电影领域引入了一种新的疯狂动物。</p><p> 《Slotherhouse》的剧情简介由马修·古德休 (Matthew Goodhue) 执导，预计于 8 月 30 日上映，内容如下：“高年级学生艾米丽·杨 (Emily Young) 希望当选为联谊会主席。她收养了一只可爱的树懒，认为它可以成为新的吉祥物并帮助她获胜，直到一系列死亡事件表明树懒是谋杀案的主要嫌疑人。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="《SLOTHERHOUSE》预告片 (2023)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/RZ1Vbh7aJPQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “一部关于杀手树懒的电影。算我一个吧，”一位推特用户分享道，另一位用户补充道：“你们大家，电影院又回来了。”</p><p> “你可以跑，但你不能……其实，跑就足够了。跑步绝对有效。”另一个人开玩笑说。</p><p> “它正在缓慢下降，这就是为什么我们必须等到 30 号，”第三位补充道。</p><p>查看下面对预告片的更多反应。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">八月底有一部叫《树懒屋》的电影上映，讲述的是树懒杀手的故事<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f9a5.png" alt="🦥" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />我完全赞成<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f923.png" alt="🤣